message.body: Sorry I didn't call yesterday baby! I'm so ready for this exam to be OVER!
No worries! Good luck, baby! Go kill it and then its the weekend and then YOU COME HERE!!!!!
Eeeeeeew haha. Did you like it ha?
Ummmm...it wasn't horrible. The acting was bad up until the last couple of scenes. It was funny in places I don't think it was supposed to be too. Haha
Haha interesting...hope you had a great time overall tho!
:) Glad to hear it, my love.
Yes yes!! Hope you're doing good!
Oh just peachy. Slept. Came in late, taking my time and looking forward to home, more sleep and soccer. And you. I cannot wait much longer ha
Yassss!!! We eat lots of icecream and chicken biryani! In that order.
Have I told you recently that elephants may just be my favorite wildlife animal?
Haha ok!! And yes! You did say that hah. I dont think i can get you one of those tho :-/
No. Probably not. I just watched a video of a baby elephant falling and mama and papa running over to help the little one up. Too cute. I love them!
Going to bed now baby! I love you so much! Goodnight!
That is cute :) And i love you so very much. Sleep well, darling.
